---
layout: base
title: Blog
description: Thinking, testing, and documenting what we learn about AI optimisation for Australian tourism.
---

<section>
    <h2>Blog</h2>
    <p>Thinking, testing, and documenting what we learn about AI optimisation for tourism. Updated when we have something worth saying.</p>
    
    <div class="blog-grid">
        {%- for post in collections.blog -%}
        <div class="blog-card">
            <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
            <p class="blog-date">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</p>
            <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
            <p><a href="{{ post.url }}">Read more &rarr;</a></p>
        </div>
        {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <p>Want to see what AI optimisation looks like in practice? <a href="/examples/"><strong>View our Barossa Valley results &rarr;</strong></a></p>
</section>